STATE of North Carolina
v.
Jimmy Harold SMITH. No. 145P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Jimmy Harold Smith, Pro Se. John G. Barnwell, Assistant Attorney General, Ronald L. Moore, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 11th day of March 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th day of January 2006."
